n_0 = sum_{d=1}^{p-1} co_occ_k(d) / (k-1)
    = [2 * sum_{d=1}^m (a_k + b_k * d)] / (k-1)
    = 2 * [m * a_k + b_k * m*(m+1)/2] / (k-1)

